				<wikidot:authorName>Shaggydredlocks</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1722371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Probably would have been more enjoyable if the concept didn't already reach its high point so early on with the bulleted list. Everything in the table was rather underwhelming - the notes section didn't have enough to intrigue or amuse me. It may have been more interesting to consider how the bacteria could evolve over time and produce increasingly wilder fears - that angle could help to keep building up, instead of petering out.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
