				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6409111#post-3873704</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6409111/scp-3459#post-3873704</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 14 Jul 2018 21:23:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Crocket_Lawnchair</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3205961</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>There are plenty of SCP that take a real-life thing and make it an anomaly. I've heard of shit like the fear that a duck is constantly watching you and figured it would make a perfect SCP. How do you even end up with a phobia of blue paper? What events have to transpire to give you that phobia?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
